            <title>[LU-15181] wrong LASSERT in osd_declare_write_commit()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15181</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
[13625.206311] UBSAN: Undefined behaviour in /mnt/ssdraid/xyratex/lustre-wc-rel3/lustre/osd-ldiskfs/osd_io.c:1404:2
[13625.206363] shift exponent 4096 is too large &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 32-bit type &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following piece of code seems to contain a typo:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        LASSERT(extent_bytes &amp;gt;= (1 &amp;lt;&amp;lt; osd_sb(osd)-&amp;gt;s_blocksize));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
